Western Australia is a state occupying the entire western third of Australia. It is bounded by the Indian Ocean to the north and west#Comma and the Southern Ocean to the south#Comma the Northern Territory to the north-east and South Australia to the south-east.

The park cultivates over 13#Comma000 species of Western Australian plants and contains one of the world's largest areas of natural bush land close to a city.
Jewel Cave is Western Australia's largest show cave and is home to one of the longest straw stalactites in any tourist cave in Australia.

Located deep within Talbot Bay in the Buccaneer Archipelago are the Horizontal Waterfalls. Massive tidal movements create a waterfall effect as water banks up against one side of the narrow cliff passage#Comma to be repeated on the turning tide. The falls can only be reached by boat or plane.

<card>#Newline                <image>https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6d/Good_Food_Display_-_NCI_Visuals_Online.jpg/1200px-Good_Food_Display_-_NCI_Visuals_Online.jpg</image>#Newline                <button>#Newline                <text>Manjimup Truffles</text>#Newline                <postback>^ Manjimup Truffles ^</postback>#Newline            </button>#Newline            <button>#Newline                <text>Pavlova</text>#Newline                <postback>^ Pavlova ^</postback>#Newline            </button>#Newline            <button>#Newline                <text>Wineries of WA</text>#Newline                <postback>^ Wineries of WA ^</postback>#Newline            </button>#Newline            </card>

WA is known as the key truffles region of Australia because it produces 80% of the nation’s truffles. Manjimup owes its unique flavour to the surrounding Karri Trees#Comma loamy soil and WA’s befitting climate#Comma i.e.#Comma balmy in summer#Comma and tepid and wet in winter.

Made during the visit of a Russian Ballerina- Anna Pavlova#Comma Pavlova is a traditional WA dessert cake with cream#Comma fruits and meringue. Resembling the beauty and breezy dance movements of Anna Pavlova#Comma the dessert itself is incredibly lightweight. A new cake made out of meringue and real fruit toppings than ones inside the cake of the bygone era was a trendsetter.

WA makes 20% the nation’s total wine with 6 outstanding wineries earning an international reputation for producing high#Comma consistent quality wines. Their handcrafted beer also enjoys a comparable reputation.
